WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Marine conservation needs mathematics!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Scientists use data and numbers to protect our oceans.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
We count species, measure temperatures, and track changes over time.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Every number helps us understand how to keep reefs healthy.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
You can help by learning maths and caring for our oceans!